roles.title: Full Stack Engineer
roles.description: Collaborated with clients to design, develop, and deploy custom web applications. Focused on creating responsive front-end interfaces and robust back-end solutions to meet diverse client needs. Successfully managed multiple projects from inception to launch, ensuring client satisfaction through high-quality standards and effective communication.

roles.title: Software Engineer
roles.description: Served as a lead developer for the enhancement of a psychotherapy platform, focusing on improving functionality and user experience. Spearheaded the development of a full-stack web application, optimizing performance and overseeing the product lifecycle to uphold high-quality standards.

roles.title: Software Engineer Intern
roles.description: Supported the development team in testing, troubleshooting, and refining the psychotherapy platform. Played a key role in collaborative efforts to enhance platform stability and functionality.

roles.title: Coding Instructor
roles.description: Educated students in programming fundamentals and video game development, employing interactive tools and methodologies to foster engagement and learning. Introduced innovative hands-on learning experiences to enhance coding proficiency and stimulate interest in technology.

roles.title: Learning Assistant
roles.description: Provided comprehensive support to students, facilitating a collaborative online learning environment. Adapted teaching methods to meet diverse student needs, contributing to a supportive community and enhancing student engagement.

roles.title: Teaching Assistant
roles.description: Played a vital role in the delivery of online educational content, offering timely assistance and feedback to students. Engaged in the creation and refinement of course materials, ensuring educational quality and accessibility.
